Name: Friet van Oost
Review Text: I had here the most crunchy fries that I ever had in my entire life, so so good! Also the meat croquette and the sate sauce were amazing. The staff is friendly and the prices are good. The place is a bit small but it's totally worth it for the food. This is definitely a Amsterdam snackbar gem, recommended!
